WEBVTT

00:02.915 --> 00:07.391
We are in Transylvania, in the frost-covered mountains of Romania,...

00:08.097 --> 00:10.545
...the impaled heart of vampire country,...

00:10.945 --> 00:15.068
...to find the region's most famous resident, the myth, the legend,...

00:15.237 --> 00:17.266
I am Dracula.

00:17.798 --> 00:18.493
...Count Dracula.

00:23.851 --> 00:27.792
You are now inside the most popular and famous tourist attraction in Romania,...

00:28.448 --> 00:31.907
...Bran Castle, better known in the whole world as Dracula castle.

00:32.155 --> 00:37.345
Count Dracula, as we know him, is loosely based on a legend of Vlad Dracula...

00:37.583 --> 00:39.413
...better known as "Vlad the Impaler,"...

00:39.502 --> 00:42.749
...the notorious ruler of this region in the 1400s...

00:43.112 --> 00:46.911
...known for his violent and tortuous methods of suppressing dissidents.

